{
  "id": "63969deb7e70c9001d39c0bb",
  "title": "KJ法の先にあるもの",
  "created": 1670815236,
  "updated": 1670916507,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63969deb7e70c9001d39c0bb",
      "text": "KJ法の先にあるもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7da2",
      "text": "2022-12-13 西尾泰和",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "6396a3e4aff09e0000044386",
      "text": "サイボウズラボ年末発表会",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670816741,
      "updated": 1670816755
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7da3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7da4",
      "text": "先日ロフトワークでKJ法勉強会を開催しました",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7da5",
      "text": "　Zoom+Slack+Miroでリモート開催",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7da6",
      "text": "　40人ちょいが共通の場で同時編集、面白い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7da7",
      "text": "　[https://gyazo.com/f91524b7db379139f4fde95214b49207]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7da8",
      "text": "　1時間用の講義資料を事前配布して30分の講演をした、それをこれから4分で喋る、詳しくはこちら: [KJ法勉強会@ロフトワーク]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815331
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7da9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7daa",
      "text": "川喜田二郎[川喜田二郎.icon]作ったKJ法",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dab",
      "text": "　20年で結構変わっている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670816778
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dac",
      "text": "　　前期 1967年「発想法」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dad",
      "text": "　　中期 1977年「知の探検学」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dae",
      "text": "　　後期 1988年「KJ法 渾沌をして語らしめる」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7daf",
      "text": " 「発想法」が一番有名だが、それは一番古い前期の考え方",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7db1",
      "text": " 「発想法」から10年の間に多様な目的に応用された",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7db2",
      "text": " 　「KJ法」という言葉の指す概念が広がった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7db3",
      "text": "　参加者から反響大きかったポイント",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815676
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7db4",
      "text": "　　大勢で付箋に書き出してそれを大勢でまとめる活動を経験したことある？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815698
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7db5",
      "text": "　　これを「KJ法」だと認識してる人が多い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670816800
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7db6",
      "text": "　　ところが[川喜田二郎.icon]自身は「まず一人でやって力量が充分に成熟していないと望ましくない妥協がおこる」と言っている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670916507
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7db7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7db8",
      "text": "「望ましくない妥協」とは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7db9",
      "text": "　例えば先輩と後輩がペアで活動してるとする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dba",
      "text": "　[https://gyazo.com/e249b88f436ff3bf9d15d99579239ae5]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dbb",
      "text": "　先輩が「これは丸だ」と言った",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815572
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dbc",
      "text": "　　この時に後輩は「私の視点からは四角に見える」と言えるか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dbd",
      "text": "　\t(丸なの？私は四角な気がするけど…でも先輩が丸だっていうならそれが正解なのかな…何が正解かわからない…)とくちごもってしまってないか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dbe",
      "text": "　　これが[* 望ましくない妥協]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dbf",
      "text": "　\t円柱は丸でも四角でもない。「丸だ」「四角だ」の両方の意見が合わさらなければ円柱だとわからない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815738
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dc0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dc1",
      "text": "参加者からのフィードバック",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dc2",
      "text": "\t[human.icon]「[心理的安全性]」「[組織の多様性]」の領域で語られていることをまた別の視点から考えている感",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dc3",
      "text": "\tまさにその通り！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815587
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dc4",
      "text": "\t >望ましくない妥協を起こさない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dc5",
      "text": "\t \tチームメンバーが自分の「異なる視点からの見え方」を話すことが必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815838
    },
    {
      "id": "6396a04daff09e0000044383",
      "text": "\t \tそれにためらいを感じない環境が必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815822,
      "updated": 1670815842
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dc6",
      "text": "\t \t=心理的安全性のある環境",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dc7",
      "text": "\t >「判断」の質を良くするためには、いくつもの違う視点からの情報と整合性を持って繋がるようにする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815785
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dc8",
      "text": "\t 　「違う視点からの情報」を集めるのは、視点の異なる多様な人がいるとやりやすくなる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815804
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dc9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dca",
      "text": "多元的組織の時代",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670816061
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dcb",
      "text": "　[価値観]の軸がたくさんある[多元的]な組織",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670816065
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dcc",
      "text": "　KJ法の考え方が新しい[チームワーク]の形のヒントになる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670816068
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dcd",
      "text": "　一方でKJ法の具体的手法は古い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dce",
      "text": "　　1967年や1988年の本にはパソコンやスマホが普及する前のやり方しか書いてない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dcf",
      "text": "　　[グループウェア]ももちろんない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670816075
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dd0",
      "text": "　　今回やったこと： Miroを使ってリアルタイムに遠隔地の人と一緒にワークショップ！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815868
    },
    {
      "id": "6396a07eaff09e0000044384",
      "text": "　　 そんなやり方、[川喜田二郎.icon]の本のどこにも書いてない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815871,
      "updated": 1670815887
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dd1",
      "text": "　今必要なこと",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dd2",
      "text": "　　KJ法の考え方を再発見しつつ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dd3",
      "text": "　　KJ法の手法を現代的な道具を使ってアップデート",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815925
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dd4",
      "text": "　アップデートの主体は",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670816102
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dd5",
      "text": "  川喜田二郎ではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dd6",
      "text": "  今を生きる私たちがやるしかない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815934
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dd7",
      "text": " どうやってやるのか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815941
    },
    {
      "id": "6396a0c0aff09e0000044385",
      "text": "　 それぞれ我流を作って情報交換するのが良い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815937,
      "updated": 1670815943
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dd8",
      "text": "　　なぜなら",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dd9",
      "text": "   働き方も価値観も多様化してる時代",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7dda",
      "text": "   誰か一人が「これが正解のやり方です」とやるのはうまくいかない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670816119
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7ddb",
      "text": "   個々人が自分にフィットしたやり方を探していく必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670816137
    },
    {
      "id": "63969e03aff09e0000ad7ddc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670815236,
      "updated": 1670815236
    },
    {
      "id": "6396a445aff09e0000044387",
      "text": "まとめ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670816838,
      "updated": 1670816839
    },
    {
      "id": "6396a447aff09e0000044389",
      "text": "　[伝統とは火を守ることであり、灰を崇拝することではない] --- グスタフ・マーラー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670816839,
      "updated": 1670816877
    },
    {
      "id": "6396a46daff09e000004438a",
      "text": "　今必要なこと",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670816878,
      "updated": 1670816924
    },
    {
      "id": "6396a497aff09e000004438b",
      "text": "　　KJ法の考え方を再発見しつつ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670816919,
      "updated": 1670816919
    },
    {
      "id": "6396a497aff09e000004438c",
      "text": "　　KJ法の手法を現代的な道具を使ってアップデート",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670816919,
      "updated": 1670816919
    },
    {
      "id": "6396a4b1aff09e000004438d",
      "text": "　　個々人が自分にフィットしたやり方を探していく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670816946,
      "updated": 1670816946
    },
    {
      "id": "6396a446aff09e0000044388",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670816839,
      "updated": 1670816839
    }
  ]
}